room_title: Escape room "Code Name: Undead - Area 52" by The Exit Game in San Antonio
room_address: 5720 Bandera Rd STE 23, San Antonio, TX 78238
room_description: Can you find the cure to prevent the apocalypse? With the government officials plotting a conspiracy, will you do what's necessary to escape quarantine? The experiment has gone terribly wrong. You must collect all scientist clearance badges, find the detonation switch and locate the cure before time runs out!
